---
title: Carb Smart Middle Eastern Beef Bowls with Pine Nuts and Tahini Sauce
description: With rich flavours of sesame and pine nuts, this low-starch supper is a star. Plus, leftover bulgur will work perfectly in a salad for lunch the next day.
